[self_consistency][qwen2_5_0_5b_instruct][gsm8k] sample 12/100 path 3/5 answer='Anakin caught 10 + 6 + 3 = <<10+6+3=29>>29 fish.\nLocsin caught 50 - 5 = <<50-5=45>>45 starfish.\nLocsin also caught 6 - 3 = <<6-3=3>>3 sea horses.\nAnd, Locsin caught 3 + 2 = <<3+2=5>>5 clownfish.\nTogether, Anakin and Locsin caught 29 + 45 + 5 = <<29+45+5=89>>89 fish.\n\nTherefore, Anakin and Locsin were able to catch 89 fish in total.'
