otal of 9.5 hours. The final answer is 9.5.": 1, "To calculate the total time for all the after-work activities, we'll sum up the durations of each activity:\n\n1. Yoga class: 1 hour\n2. Cooking class: 3 * 1 hour = 3 hours\n3. Cheese tasting event: 0.5 hours (half of a hour)\n4. Museum tour: 0.5 * 3 hours = 1.5 hours\n5. Errands: 2 hours\n\nNow, let's add them together:\n\nTotal = Yoga + Cooking + Cheese Tasting Event + Museum Tour + Errands\nTotal = 1 hour + 3 hours + 0.5 hours + 1.5 hours + 2 hours\nTotal = 7.5 hours\n\nSo, all of Peyton's after-work activities will take 7.5 hours.": 1}
