e between Joey's score and Marcy's score:\n\nJoey's score - Marcy's score = (214 - 10) = 204\n\nTo find out how many points Joey is winning by, we subtract Marcy's total points from Joey's final score:\n\nJoys score - Marcy's total points = 204 - 214 = -10\n\nSo Joey is losing by 10 points. Therefore, Joey is currently losing by 10 points.": 1}
