[self_consistency][qwen2_5_0_5b_instruct][gsm8k] sample 44/100 path 1/5 answer="First, let's calculate the total number of vlogs Emma made during those three weeks:\n\nWeek 1: 18 vlogs\nWeek 2: 21 vlogs\nWeek 3: 15 vlogs\n\nTotal from 3 weeks = 18 + 21 + 15 = 54 vlogs\n\nEmma wants to finish with 72 vlogs per month, so we subtract the total she already made from the monthly goal:\n\nMonthly goal: 72 vlogs\nAlready made: 54 vlogs\n\nVlogs needed to reach the monthly goal = Monthly goal - Already made\nVlogs needed = 72 - 54 = 18 vlogs\n\nTherefore, Emma should aim to make 18 additional vlogs to meet her goal of 72 vlogs per month."
