[self_consistency][qwen2_5_0_5b_instruct][gsm8k] sample 98/100 path 1/5 answer='First, we calculate how much money each person raised:\n\nKim raised $320 more than Alexandra:\n$430 + $320 = $750\n\nMaryam raised $400 more than Sarah:\n$300 + $400 = $700\n\nNow, we sum up their individual totals:\nKim: $750\nAlexandra: $430\nSarah: $300\nMaryam: $700\n\nTotal amount raised by all three:\n$750 + $430 + $300 + $700 = $2,380\n\nSo, the total amount raised by the girls was $2,380.'
