[self_consistency][qwen2_5_0_5b_instruct][gsm8k] sample 33/100 path 2/3 answer='Ray initially had 25 lollipops. After keeping 5 for himself, he gave away \\(25 - 5 = 20\\) lollipops to his friends. Since he has four friends, we divide the remaining lollipops equally among them, so each friend received \\(20 \\div 4 = 5\\) lollipops. Therefore, each of his friends received 5 lollipops.'
