[self_consistency][qwen2_5_0_5b_instruct][gsm8k] sample 44/100 path 1/3 answer='To find out how many more vlogs Emma needs to make to reach her goal of making 72 vlogs per month, we start by calculating the total number of vlogs she has already made:\n\nFirst week: 18 vlogs\nSecond week: 21 vlogs\nThird week: 15 vlogs\n\nTotal made so far: 18 + 21 + 15 = 54 vlogs\n\nNow, subtract the number of vlogs she has already made from her target to find out how many more she needs to make:\n\n72 (target) - 54 (already made) = 18 vlogs\n\nTherefore, Emma needs to make 18 more vlogs to complete her goal of making 72 vlogs per month.'
