[self_consistency][qwen2_5_0_5b_instruct][gsm8k] sample 91/100 path 1/3 answer="Let's break it down:\n\n1. Eve originally had 20 pieces of pomelos.\n2. She was left with \\( \\frac{1}{4} \\) of what she originally had, so she gave away \\( 20 \\times \\frac{1}{4} = 5 \\) pieces of pomelos.\n\nTherefore, Eve gave away 5 pieces of pomelos."
